dct_creator_sm: Netherlands Antilles. Dienst van het Kadaster
dct_description_sm: This map is Sheet 4 of the map series Topographic maps of Aruba 1:25,000, 1995. This digital version has been scanned, cropped to the map area, georeferenced, and published by Land Info. Contour intervals are shown at 10 meters. Text is in English and Dutch. The original print sheet was published as part of the map series Topografische kaart van de Nederlandse Antillen en Aruba 1:25,000, republished in Amsterdam by Rudolf Muller in 1995. The map is based on fieldwork by the Dienst van het Kadaster (Nederlandse Antillen) and aerial photography flown by KLM Aerocarto.
